The paper deals with the problem of RDF stream reasoning, which is related to databases (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of modern distributed computing frameworks such as Apache Spark and Apache Flink also suggests a connection to data science (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the trade-off between language expressiveness and system scalability, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
